title: Wall Street Breakfast June 16: Stock Futures Reverse Post-Fed Rally as Traders Reassess Biggest Rate Hike Since '94
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stock futures reverse post-Fed rally as traders reassess biggest rate hike since '94. Musk expected to confirm ownership push in Twitter meeting - WSJ. Exxon responds to Biden's request for solutions to the oil refining crisis. Binance looks to hire 2,000 as other crypto firms cut their headcount. Catch today’s WSB article here.
